================================================================================
README
================================================================================
Overview

This repository contains the complete analytical code, de-identified dataset, and supplementary materials for the manuscript:

When Knowledge Does Not Translate into Practice: Innovation Readiness as a Missing Capability Layer in Constrained Pharmaceutical Systems

================================================================================
CRITICAL ALIGNMENT STATEMENT (SAP + MANUSCRIPT + STROBE)
================================================================================

All analyses, variables, transformations, and statistical procedures in this repository:

STRICTLY FOLLOW SAP v1.0.

Specifically:

No BCa bootstrap methods were used
All confidence intervals for correlations are computed using Fisher z-transformation only
No random seed dependency is used or required
Nested model comparison follows ΔR² + ΔAIC + ΔBIC framework with F-change test reported as auxiliary inference only
All effect sizes follow predefined SAP hierarchy (η², f², Cohen’s d, r)
All variables are treated as formative composite indices (non-latent constructs)
================================================================================
REPRODUCIBILITY GUARANTEE
================================================================================

This project is fully reproducible under the following conditions:

Python 3.12+
Fixed package versions defined in requirements.txt
Deterministic execution ensured via fixed environment specification (no stochastic procedures requiring seeds)
All preprocessing steps are explicitly encoded in Innovation_Capability_Analysis.py

No hidden preprocessing, no external transformations, and no manual post-hoc adjustments were applied.

